title: Converse Rubber Tracks: Plants and Animals performs "Lightshow"
description: Montréal, QC band Plants and Animals tore through a live version of their song "Lightshow" at our Montréal pop-up Converse Rubber Tracks studio. The track is from their 2012 album, The End of That out now on Secret City Records
